title: The Two You's - Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Two You's - Joel Osteen
description:
There’s a battle constantly taking place on the inside between the two yous. The Scripture calls this the battle between the flesh and the spirit.We all face the temptation to give into our flesh, but Joel will encourage you to live powerfully in the spirit. You are not walking alone; God wants to empower you to live by His spirit each day.Philippians 2:13 says, “God is working in you, giving you the desire to obey Him and the power to do what is right.” Right now the Most High God is working in you.Instead of giving into weak, insecure, compromising you, you’ll be empowered to be the strong, disciplined, confident you! Instead of walking in negativity and discouragement, you’ll be empowered to live faith filled and have big dreams again. As you learn discipline to feed your spirit, you will step into a new season of growth and favor!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
